    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="well">
    <p>3.1. Which presentation do you prefer?<p>
    <label class="radio-inline"><input type="radio" name="<%= debate2 %>-layout_v_formatted-overall" value="<%= s1.first %>-much_better">A is much better</label>
